{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "失落历史～尘封的真相～第3话 秘密调查与行动",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "王国军开始肆无忌惮地破坏大自然。\\n伊莉雅认为他们心怀不轨，\\n便试着窃听军方的通信讯号。得知他们\\n准备将王都和龙一起毁灭的作战计划后，\\n一行人为阻止其计划而向王都进发。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120201_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "查到伊莉雅的下落了吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120204_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "还没有。她似乎没回后街的房子，\\n目前依然行踪不明……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120201_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "到底藏到哪里去了。\\n另一个女人呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120204_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "也没有找到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120201_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "如此一来，她们两个在一起的\\n可能性很高。瞎找也不是个办法，\\n差不多该想想别的主意了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120201_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "把伊莉雅逼出来的方法……\\n对了，比如这种……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "魔力相当紊乱，\\n这样下去的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "泽拉森林刚被烧，\\n这回又是宇基湖遭到污染。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "他们开始肆无忌惮地破坏自然。\\n那些龙已经怒火中烧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "他们是想削弱龙的力量吗？\\n但我觉得这种挑衅行为很危险。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是啊。我有不祥的预感。\\n稍微调查一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "诶？要怎么调查？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "用秘密工具。\\n不过需要维修就是了。\\n莫尔提斯，你能帮我一个忙吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "当然。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "我说伊莉雅！\\n不可以做危险的事……\\n你有没有在听啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "（王国在打什么主意呢？\\n希望不会一发不可收拾……）",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "几天后",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "锵锵！窃听系统！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "窃听……系统？\\n那是什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "只要有了这个机器，\\n就能偷听人们的对话了。\\n我们用这个来偷听军方的策略。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "还、还能这样！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "没有危险倒还好……\\n不会被对方发现吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这一点不用担心。\\n但如果你想听详细的说明，\\n我倒是很乐意讲给你听哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "唉……就算听了\\n也听不懂，还是算了。\\n没有危险的话就开始吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "好。那就启动了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "谢谢你昨晚\\n让我过得如梦似幻，\\n我对你的感情更……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "嗯？不是这个，\\n也不知道是哪个贵族\\n在表达爱意。唔……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "……很顺利。\\n虽然受到了龙的干扰，\\n但一切都在预料之中。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "噢，好像是这个。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "这下挑衅应该到位了。\\n另一件事进展如何？\\n没被市民发现吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "这声音……没错，是奥古斯。\\n似乎是在和部下说话。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "另一件事也很顺利，\\n100个都已经在王都里安装完毕。\\n就等那一天了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "在王都里安装了100个什么？\\n那天又是指什么事？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "之后就等龙被激怒，\\n攻入王都了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "到时候，王都里事先\\n安装好的魔力炸弹一爆炸，\\n就能解决掉那些家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01",
                "110368_01",
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "奥古斯",
            "context": "那我等着那一天，辛苦了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01",
                "110368_01",
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "士兵",
            "context": "是！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "他们是为了挑衅龙\\n才破坏了森林湖泊啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "龙攻入王都的时候，\\n那里就会被魔力炸弹\\n炸成一片火海……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "为了不让龙察觉到\\n有什么异乎寻常的动向，\\n他们甚至没有告知市民吗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "把人命当成什么了！\\n果然腐败透顶！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "所以要怎么办，伊莉雅？\\n放任不管吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "其实……我们自己远走高飞\\n倒也不是不可以。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "但那样就和奥古斯没区别了，\\n那种只考虑自己的人渣……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "既然知道了\\n有数百万生命遭到威胁，\\n我就不能袖手旁观！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我想去救人。\\n你愿意和我一起来吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "当然。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "先等一下。\\n你说救人，要怎么救？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "拆除所有的炸弹。既然是魔力炸弹，\\n只要让魔力本身失效，就能轻易拆除。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "隐藏炸弹的位置\\n只要看地图和建筑物，\\n就能猜个大概。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "他们应该会设在龙攻入时\\n能有效炸到龙的地方。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "要拆除所有的炸弹……\\n光凭我们四个人\\n真的能办到吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "不知道。不过既然\\n我们知道了这件事，\\n就不能见死不救。对吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "是啊……你要说的我都懂，\\n但……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "你是在担心我吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "是啊。作为养育你的监护人，\\n比起几百万别人的性命，\\n更在乎你一个人的命啊。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "这就是……爱吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "是啊。不过，正因为我从小\\n在梅奈的这种爱里长大，\\n所以我很清楚。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "即将成为牺牲品的那些人\\n一定也有各自所爱的、\\n所珍视的事物吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "我能想象得到\\n他们被剥夺那些存在的痛苦。\\n所以我才要阻止这一切。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "抱歉……是我糊涂了。\\n你是对的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110368_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "梅奈",
            "context": "而且只要我跟你一起去，\\n保护好你就是了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110369_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莫尔提斯",
            "context": "我也会保护伊莉雅。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "塞西娅",
            "context": "我也一起去。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "谢谢你们。那事不宜迟，\\n我们趁着晚上行动，\\n把炸弹全部解除，怎么样？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110367_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "伊莉雅",
            "context": "现在出发的话，\\n正好能在行人变少的时候到。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20423_04_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100009_01"
            ],
